类 ServletPathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy

    public class ServletPathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy
extends PathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy
    Extends PathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy that also uses ServletContext.getMimeType(String) to resolve file extensions.
    从以下版本开始:
    3.2
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

    • 构造器概要

      ServletPathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy(ServletContext servletContext, Map<String,MediaType> mediaTypes)

      • ServletPathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy

        public ServletPathExtensionContentNegotiationStrategy(ServletContext context)
        Create an instance without any mappings to start with. Mappings may be added later when extensions are resolved through ServletContext.getMimeType(String) or via JAF.
